# Conditional Execution ğŸ¯

```groovy
stage('Deploy') {
    when {
        branch 'main'
    }
    steps {
        sh './deploy.sh'
    }
}
```

## Conditions

| Condition | Example |
|-----------|--------|
| `branch` | `branch 'main'` |
| `tag` | `tag 'v*'` |
| `expression` | `expression { return true }` |

# Build Parameters ğŸ“‹

```groovy
parameters {
    string(name: 'VERSION', defaultValue: '1.0.0')
    choice(name: 'ENV', choices: ['dev', 'prod'])
    booleanParam(name: 'DEPLOY', defaultValue: true)
}

stages {
    stage('Deploy') {
        when { expression { params.DEPLOY } }
        steps {
            echo "Deploying ${params.VERSION}"
        }
    }
}
```

# Shared Libraries ğŸ“š

## vars/deployApp.groovy

```groovy
def call(String env) {
    sh "./deploy.sh ${env}"
}
```

## Using Library

```groovy
@Library('my-lib') _

pipeline {
    agent any
    stages {
        stage('Deploy') {
            steps { deployApp('prod') }
        }
    }
}
```

# Docker Pipeline ğŸ³

```groovy
pipeline {
    agent {
        docker {
            image 'node:20'
            args '-v $HOME/.npm:/root/.npm'
        }
    }
    stages {
        stage('Build') {
            steps {
                sh 'npm ci'
                sh 'npm run build'
            }
        }
    }
}
```

# Notifications ğŸ“«

```groovy
post {
    success {
        slackSend(color: 'good', message: 'Build passed!')
    }
    failure {
        slackSend(color: 'danger', message: 'Build failed!')
    }
}
```

## Post Conditions

| Condition | When |
|-----------|------|
| `always` | Always |
| `success` | Passed |
| `failure` | Failed |

# Complete Pipeline ğŸš€

```groovy
pipeline {
    agent { docker 'node:20' }

    stages {
        stage('Build') {
            steps { sh 'npm run build' }
        }
        stage('Test') {
            parallel {
                stage('Unit') { steps { sh 'npm test' } }
                stage('Lint') { steps { sh 'npm run lint' } }
            }
        }
        stage('Deploy') {
            when { branch 'main' }
            steps { sh './deploy.sh' }
        }
    }
}
```
